GCompris d yiwen useγẓan n usegmi ay yesεan aṭas yiqeddicen i warrac ger 2 d 10 yiseggasen.

Iqeddiccen-is tikwal d iwuraren, maca yalas d usegmisnen. Ad d-tafem iqeddicen deg yiḥricen yetteddun :

    * tiwfit (tagrut) n uselkim : anasiw, amumed, imussa n wamumed, …
    * tusnakt : allas n tifelwa (tiduba), uḍḍun, tifelwa s snat yinekcam, tujjurt, …
    * tussniwin : tazarurt (trisiti), asinef, allus n waman, tanettabt, …
    * tarakalt : sers timura deg tkarḍa
    * uraren : tiruẓiyen n uqerruy, tiddest, takatut (tacfawit, timektit), …
    * taγuri : alaγmu n tγuri
    * nayeḍ : taγuri n temret (asrag), tijeggirin (tiklutin) yettwassnen s talγa n puzzle, unuγ amawayan, asnulfu n tinnaγ inemussan …

GCompris yesεa ugar n 100 yiqeddicen u mazal ar sdat. GCompris d aseγẓan ilelli, ihi tzemreḍ ad t-tbeddleḍ s lebγi-k(m) neγ i usnerni-s, neγ ahat ad asen-t-tefkeḍ i warrac n umaḍal merra.

